            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1706875523257-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper has softened, add the<strong> sliced garlic</strong> and your <strong>'Nduja</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for a further 3-4 min, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1706875526785-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
