    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained tagliatelle</strong> to the pan and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your<strong> creamy 'Nduja & red pepper sauce with fresh tagliatelle</strong></p>",
