      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy 'Nduja & red pepper sauce with fresh tagliatelle </strong>with the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the lettuce with a little <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
